KNOWN ISSUES:
 * Using some fonts for the tag cloud will result in OutOfMemoryErrors. If this
   happens, just select a different font.

Version 1.1.0, January 27, 2011
 * Select a color scheme for tag clouds.
 * Users can define their own color schemes by editing the
   ~/.tagerator/colorschemes.txt file.
 * Tags and counts are cached after each run.
 * Results of the most recent run are shown at startup.

Version 1.0.0, January 13, 2011
 * Initial release.
